<br>
Double-dipping isn't allowed and that is one of the reasons both BotS and NB made a public declaration on this board that any of their wizards caught MBing a rotation mob would be booted. If 6-7 people that are unguilded can kill statue, then yeah, they DO get on the rotation. Since you can't be allied for some rotations, people from guilds that got together to kill something like statue would be causing a shitstorm, because they would be invalidating their own guilds posting status as an independent entity.<br>
<br>
Its possible, sure. And I would congratulate them if someone did.<br>
